    <item>
      <title>特朗普的“美国制造”比特币威胁中国巨头比特大陆的统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/trump-s-made-in-usa-bitcoin-relies-on-chinese-rig-maker-bitmain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，一家中国公司一直主宰着加密货币领域最赚钱的领域之一。日益加剧的政治紧张局势以及唐纳德·特朗普重夺白宫的可能性，对这一统治构成了前所未有的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/trump-s-made-in-usa-bitcoin-relies-on-chinese-rig-maker-bitmain</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“危险先例”震动智利可再生能源市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/-dangerous-precedent-rattles-chile-s-renewable-energy-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项立法变化有可能破坏可再生能源领域世界上最安全的赌注之一——智利的一项激励计划，该计划吸引了由贝莱德公司和摩根大通公司支持的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/-dangerous-precedent-rattles-chile-s-renewable-energy-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消费者支出疲软 鼎泰丰将关闭中国门店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/din-tai-fung-to-close-china-outlets-amid-weak-consumer-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾饺子连锁店鼎泰丰将关闭中国大陆十多家门店，为了吸引越来越节俭的中国消费者，中国大陆市场餐厅之间展开了残酷的价格战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/din-tai-fung-to-close-china-outlets-amid-weak-consumer-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:56:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Paytm 股价因新一轮监管审查报告而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/paytm-shares-drop-after-report-on-fresh-regulatory-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称，印度市场监管机构要求 Paytm 提供更多与首次公开募股相关的信息，这可能会加剧这家金融科技先驱的监管问题，此后 Paytm 股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/paytm-shares-drop-after-report-on-fresh-regulatory-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:53:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科学家称 Mpox 传播可预防</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/scientists-say-mpox-spread-preventable-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲中部地区爆发了 mpox 疫情，导致数百人死亡，数千人感染。科学家们表示，失去机会和缺乏资金导致了这种致命病毒的传播。彭博新闻社的 Janice Kew 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/scientists-say-mpox-spread-preventable-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:46:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
